50|$|The State shall {{endeavor}} to have credit information provided {{at the least}} cost to all participants and shall ensure <b>the</b> <b>protection</b> <b>of</b> <b>consumer</b> rights and <b>the</b> existence of fair competition in the industry at all times. An efficient credit information system will also enable financial institutions to reduce their over-all credit risk, contributing to a healthier and more stable financial system.|$|R
